name: Elemental Worlds (Panobato)
description:
Patchouli lost control of her magic, and accidentally formed different worlds based on the different elements. She needs Marisa's help to get it back, and Marisa needs her help to get back safely.

A precision platformer made for the Touhou Pride Jam 4. This is my first full Unity project, it's certainly not the most polished game, but I'm happy with it, no matter how haphazard it seems. Hope you enjoy!
